data.description: Exceptionally well-maintained, this 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence boasts updated flooring throughout and bespoke wood finishes. The kitchen has undergone recent renovations, featuring state-of-the-art appliances such as a stove and dishwasher. Step into the backyard retreat, complete with a covered patio adorned with brand-new string lights and ceiling fans, as well as a fire pit perfect for gatherings or tranquil stargazing evenings. Furthermore, there's a covered shed with built-in shelves, ideal for storing tools or indulging your creative pursuits.    But that's not all! Venture beyond the fence to discover your private sanctuary along the Apalachee River. Impress your guests with an outdoor pizza oven, smoker, and grill, elevating your entertaining game and earning envy from friends and family.    Additional Features: Updated Fence Stain, Insulated Piping for Outdoor Hoses, Herb Garden, Established Rosemary, and Strawberry Patch yielding yearly fruits. Located in an excellent school district, and conveniently close to shopping and walking trails. Don't miss out Co contact us today!
